+in+vasculitis&amp;author=E+Miloslavsky&amp;author=S+Unizony&amp;publication_year=2014&amp;journal=Rheum+Dis+Clin+North+Am&amp;pages=11-26&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.rdc.2013.10.006&amp;pmid=24268007">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">4.</div><div id="r4" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Misra DP, Shenoy SN. Cardiac involvement in primary systemic vasculitis and potential drug therapies to reduce cardiovascular risk. <em>Rheumatol Int</em> 2017;37(1):151–167.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00296-016-3435-1">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26886388/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Cardiac+involvement+in+primary+systemic+vasculitis+and+potential+drug+therapies+to+reduce+cardiovascular+risk&amp;author=DP+Misra&amp;author=SN+Shenoy&amp;publication_year=2017&amp;journal=Rheumatol+Int&amp;pages=151-167&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs00296-016-3435-1&amp;pmid=26886388">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">5.</div><div id="r5" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Raman SV, Aneja A, Jarjour WN. CMR in inflammatory vasculitis. <em>J Cardiovasc Magn Reson</em> 2012;14(1):82. <a href="https://jcmr-online.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1532-429X-14-82">https://jcmr-online.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1532-429X-14-82</a>. Published November 30, 2012.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1186/1532-429X-14-82">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23199343/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=CMR+in