ar&amp;author=V+Agarwal&amp;publication_year=2016&amp;journal=Trop+Doct&amp;pages=180-186&amp;doi=10.1177%2F0049475515624031&amp;pmid=27694317">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">60.</div><div id="r60" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Goodfield NE, Bhandari S, Plant WD, Morley-Davies A, Sutherland GR. Cardiac involvement in Wegener’s granulomatosis. <em>Br Heart J</em> 1995;73(2):110–115.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1136/hrt.73.2.110">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7696016/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Cardiac+involvement+in+Wegener%E2%80%99s+granulomatosis&amp;author=NE+Goodfield&amp;author=S+Bhandari&amp;author=WD+Plant&amp;author=A+Morley-Davies&amp;author=GR+Sutherland&amp;publication_year=1995&amp;journal=Br+Heart+J&amp;pages=110-115&amp;doi=10.1136%2Fhrt.73.2.110&amp;pmid=7696016">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">61.</div><div id="r61" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Stone JH, Merkel PA, Spiera R, et al. Rituximab versus cyclophosphamide for ANCA-associated vasculitis. <em>N Engl J Med</em> 2010;363(3):221–232.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1056/NEJMoa0909905">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20647199/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Rituximab+versus+cyclophosphamide+for+ANCA-associated+vasculitis&amp;author=JH+Stone&amp;author=PA+Merkel&amp;author=R+Spiera&amp;publication_year=2010&amp;journal=N+Engl+J+Med&amp;pages=221-232&amp;doi=10.1056%2FN